OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Taliban       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fannounce new rules for     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffemale students            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Afghan universities will be segregated 
OL,6, by gender, and a new Islamic dress code
OL,7, will be introduced, the Taliban said on
OL,8, Sunday.                                
OL,10,FHigher Education Minister Abdul Baqi   
OL,11,FHaqqani indicated women would be       
OL,12,Fallowed to study, but not alongside    
OL,13,Fmen.                                   
OL,15,FHe also announced a review of subjects 
OL,16,Ftaught.                                
OL,18,FWomen and girls were banned from       
OL,19,Fschools and universities under Taliban 
OL,20,Frule between 1996 and 2001.            
